mp": 1780468963}, {"pid": 870474538, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 144, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-03 14:46", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "你们到底在怕什么  现在不是符合预期么<br/>掉下来能V上去的都是科技<br/>这不是在反复确认这个事实给市场看么", "lou": 2922, "content_length": 91, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780469178}, {"pid": 870474843, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 75, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-03 14:48", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=870474580,45974302,6421]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=38140916]huohuo277[/uid] (2026-06-03 14:46):[/b]<br/><br/>谁还敢做多啊[/quote]<br/>为什么不敢  现在就是告诉你  做多科技才有前途 你不做就是不行  你们到底看不看我的小剧场的<br/>明牌就是把你诱多进来 要么你就别做这个市场，不然要赚钱就只能被诱多进来  你说你做不做吧", "lou": 2923, "content_length": 167, "reply_to": 870474580, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780469318}, {"pid": 870476353, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 56, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-03 14:59", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=870476085,45974302,6425]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=46132]nangle[/uid] (2026-06-03 14:57):[/b]<br/><br/>煤炭、电力也V了啊。。[/quote]<br/>实在不懂怎么和你们说了 都说了他是主线趋势的防御方向 你都不理解是什么意思嘛 你看看他们几点拉起来的  对应盘面如何", "lou": 2924, "content_length": 111, "reply_to": 870476085, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780469982}, {"pid": 870477374, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 71, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-03 15:06", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=870476590,45974302,6425]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=64973700]SpamSender[/uid] (2026-06-03 15:01):[/b]<br/><br/>今天拉煤炭电力，明天要拉什么抵抗科技大军[/quote]<br/>你们都没搞懂  为什么要抵抗科技大军  到底为什么啊 <br/>现在就是告诉你 不管拉的是光和半导体  还是电力  都是进攻方向。只是进攻里面的轮动而已。", "lou": 2925, "content_length": 129, "reply_to": 870476590, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780470386}, {"pid": 870479489, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 184, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-03 15:21", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "我觉得你们水平还是太过于低下，分享盘口语言没什么意思<br/>就说一句 你们自己去看一下这段时间的 金属 白酒 AI软 到今天商航都是一些什么个股表现<br/>然后自己计算一下他们对应搅动了多少活跃资金<br/>最后算出如果要让半导体止跌还要多少资金<br/>就能算出这波震荡筑底什么时候结束了。<br/>我直接说出来 你们肯定到处去说 然后又不懂是为什么 就拿一个数字满世界的问。", "lou": 2926, "content_length": 314, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780471316}, {"pid": 870479674, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 40, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-03 15:23", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=870479164,45974302,6429]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=42821487]我是一只猪阿[/uid] (2026-06-03 15:19):[/b]<br/><br/>[img]./mon_202606/03/jmQ6-b6sgZeT3cSlc-sg.jpg[/img][/quote]<br/>哪怕是1% 他还是极低利率  华尔街不会放过这块肥肉的<br/>但是这个措施能稍微延缓160这个坎。如果加息的话<br/>这个毕竟是传说中的日元斩杀线。", "lou": 2927, "content_length": 126, "reply_to": 870479164, "14": {"13": 1}, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780471390}, {"pid": 870479776, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 34, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-03 15:23", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=870479236,45974302,6429]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=62146147]孫笑川228[/uid] (2026-06-03 15:20):[/b]<br/><br/>[img]./mon_202606/03/jmQ6-j6qlZeT3cSyw-24o.webp.medium.jpg[/img]<br/>几个意思？<br/>[img]./mon_202606/03/jmQ6-7gvjKdT3cSkf-go.webp.medium.jpg[/img][/quote]<br/>昨天刚说了 这些指数ETF已经进了不少科技 科技拉他们就拉。", "lou": 2928, "content_length": 58, "reply_to": 870479236, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780471439}, {"pid": 870480673, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 213, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-03 15:30", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "现在震荡筑底就是两个事<br/>一个是不断的把你们这帮追高科技的韭菜变成基石<br/>二是不断的打击老登的底线，比如前天巴菲特基金进了谷歌的，让老登再也没有借口了，然后就是茅台不断的被科技股超过价格<br/><br/>不论什么手段，最后都会让赛道拥挤，一致性在最高位置一定会迎来监管，我们的市场就是这样<br/>所以 我们只能提前拥抱一致性，到时候出现了再跑  只要跑得快一点，利润垫足够那我就是赢家。<br/><br/>市场就是这么明确<br/><br/>你们丧失的只是本心而已。", "lou": 2929, "content_length": 386, "14": {"13": 2}, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780471854}, {"pid": 870481595, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 66, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-03 15:37", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=870481323,45974302,6431]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=41445191]gatsbyL[/uid] (2026-06-03 15:35):[/b]<br/><br/>说的对狼大，坚定持有到4300以上，锂电和碳酸锂期货这块您怎么看，锂矿都回调这么久了，一点反弹的意思都没有[/quote]<br/>你打开碳酸锂期货 放到第一个 他止跌  这个方向就能看<br/>否则不看", "lou": 2930, "content_length": 59, "reply_to": 870481323, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780472266}, {"pid": 870482337, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 8192, "score": 77, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-03 15:43", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=870480235,45974302,6430]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=6313142]暮残[/uid] (2026-06-03 15:27):[/b]<br/><br/>亨通为什么这么硬，长飞都破板了<br/>大盘炸成这个样子，纹丝不动，甚至主力还补了封单[/quote]<br/><br/>[img]./mon_202606/03/jmQ6-4mrcK7T1kSa6-1h.jpg[/img]<br/>呵呵", "lou": 2931, "content_length": 45, "attachs": [{"attachurl": "mon_202606/03/jmQ6-4mrcK7T1kSa6-1h.jpg", "size": 7, "type": "img", "subid": 0, "url_utf8_org_name": "image%2epng", "dscp": "", "path": "mon_202606/03", "name": "jmQ6-4mrcK7T1kSa6-1h.jpg", "ext": "jpg", "thumb": "56"}], "reply_to": 870480235, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780472607}, {"pid": 870484832, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 71, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-03 16:02", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=870484520,45974302,6434]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=10253715]stephaniel[/uid] (2026-06-03 15:59):[/b]<br/><br/>[img]./mon_202606/03/jmQ6-jheoK2mT1kShs-12m.jpg[/img]感慨一下，以前这些票大半都是做刀具的，现在都已经是高贵的ai硬件股了。真是一遇ai，鸡犬升天。这个故事告诉我们，不管是事业还是炒股，围绕ai主线会让你更值钱！[/quote]<br/>这不算什么 你看看张小泉 高贵的剪光缆金剪刀<br/>市场不正规就是这样了  所以做好投机就行 我不考虑投资", "lou": 2932, "content_length": 93, "reply_to": 870484520, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780473733}, {"pid": 870586604, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 65, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-04 13:08", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "移动电子减半了  剩下的等开蛊<br/>类比红富含那种。", "lou": 2933, "content_length": 42, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780549722}, {"pid": 870587289, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 86, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-04 13:15", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "你们可能不懂我在做什么  我在做老黄的演讲路线。", "lou": 2934, "content_length": 44, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780550138}, {"pid": 870587575, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 65, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-04 13:18", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=870587395,45974302,6477]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=38700657]流星桐[/uid] (2026-06-04 13:16):[/b]<br/><br/>懂了，现在老黄去了韩国那里[s:ac:哭笑]现在老黄喊单呢[/quote]<br/>嗯 聪明 存储扩产方向[s:ac:blink]", "lou": 2935, "content_length": 21, "reply_to": 870587395, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780550301}, {"pid": 870588708, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 45, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-04 13:29", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=870588601,45974302,6480]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=65329649]zippo578[/uid] (2026-06-04 13:28):[/b]<br/><br/>此时此刻必须给黄线打call<br/>加！油！啊！[/quote]<br/>黄线被吸血太狠了 微盘股要止跌才行。最近也没有净增量投放<br/>筑底需要他们止跌。", "lou": 2936, "content_length": 77, "reply_to": 870588601, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780550973}, {"pid": 870589120, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 89, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-04 13:33", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "其实从老黄在台北喊单后那个票直接起飞 你们就应该懂了  这两天的光也是老黄在喊单<br/>所以他去小韩那边只可能动存储  哪怕明天没说存储  至少今天的埋伏是吃到了 没说就走就行了 <br/>这种是超短短打思路。<br/>长期逻辑没什么变化  这只是我个人的短打思路", "lou": 2937, "content_length": 214, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780551211}, {"pid": 870589849, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 64, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-04 13:40", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=870589311,45974302,6481]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67143809]Rzzz二号机[/uid] (2026-06-04 13:35):[/b]<br/><br/>[s:pg:冻]还没筑底？ 那我这个月赚的是什么&amp;#160;&amp;#160;[/quote]<br/>我都说了 我分享的是炒股理念  尽量少亏 多赚<br/>现在赚的就是波动的钱。", "lou": 2938, "content_length": 65, "reply_to": 870589311, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780551621}, {"pid": 870590191, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 52, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-04 13:43", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "你们不用考虑太多 你们想想套定律涨的是哪些 和两长扩产最核心相关的 就是那些<br/>现在把那些做好波动的差价  不断增加筹码，等普反后的加速就行了。总比你们买那些边缘货强吧", "lou": 2939, "content_length": 154, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780551801}], "__T": {"fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "topic_misc": null, "subject": "自立自强，科学技术打头阵", "locked": 0, "recommend": 0, "quote_to": null, "quote_from": 0, "type": 36, "replies": 155495, "authorid": 150058, "postdate": 1768179906, "lastpost": 1782109382, "jdata": null, "author": "-阿狼-", "lastposter": "msjwhmxc123", "digest": 0, "lastmodify": 1782109386, "tpid": 0, "post_misc_var": {"content_length": 412, "fid": 706, "comment_id": ",854270755,860174433", "14": {"17": 1, "14": 4, "13": 4, "12": 1}, "16": "63335896,19412700,26652007,67067074,20672033,66881586,67068843,66199622,60819388,60409766,67057614,60264977,61082281,42701832,66998841,61574956,61272875,67082978,66949654,65530601,60630412,60240136,66038632,63481990,61973100,60192597,66985104,19043499,39108806,41714633,7046671,65647302,40696141,3481707,65467